Have you received a letter from the ICO? If so, act now. You are right to be suspicious when you receive correspondence from organisations you have never heard from, especially if they are demanding money. However, the ICO plays a key role in Data Protection in the UK.

As we offer Registered Office services for our <a href="https://blackandwhiteaccounting.co.uk/limited-company-services/">limited company</a> clients, we get a lot of these through our door, so we thought it would be useful to explain more below.

